Earlier you indicated that that during your first 
teaching at A&M, you did some summer research with

13:28.715 --> 13:38.913
vitamin deficiencies, perhaps in rats. Have you 
continued the work with vitamin deficiencies

13:40.876 --> 13:46.506
since then? I mean, did you switch over to 
chickens, vitamin needs for chickens, later on

13:46.546 --> 13:54.199
when you came back? Yes, yes indeed. All of my work 
since I came back from away, while I was there and

13:56.392 --> 14:07.624
since I have come back, all of my work has been with 
